### PHASE 2.5 ‚Äî Agent Harness (Option A) ‚Äî **issue #1, DONE**
> Thin `AgentHarness` over `llm_client.call_json()` / `call()` adding output
> validation + retry, console tracing, and a no-hallucination guardrail. One
> calling convention for every agent. The harness returns the original parsed dict
> (not `model_dump()`), so wrapping an agent is behaviour-preserving.

**Harness core**
- [x] T-251: Implement `agents/harness.py` ‚Äî `AgentHarness(llm_client, name, system_prompt, output_schema=None, mode="json", max_retries=2)` with `run(user_message, *, ground_against=None)`
- [x] T-253: Output validation against `output_schema`; on `ValidationError`/parse error, retry the LLM with the error appended (default 2 retries); on final failure, warn and return best-effort (pipeline stays robust)
- [x] T-254: Console tracing per call ‚Äî `[harness] agent=‚Ä¶ status=‚Ä¶ latency_ms=‚Ä¶ retries=‚Ä¶ output_valid=‚Ä¶`
- [x] T-256: Dual mode ‚Äî `mode="json"` (parse + validate) and `mode="text"` (raw string, used by persona)
- [x] T-257: `NoHallucinationGuardrail` ‚Äî flags skills/technologies in output absent from the profile (skills, certifications, experience/project technologies); wired into `run()` via `ground_against`
- [ ] T-252: (deferred) Optional input-schema validation before the LLM call ‚Äî not required by the acceptance criteria; agents build heterogeneous messages, so left for a follow-up
- [n/a] T-255: Move OTel context propagation into the harness ‚Äî **N/A on `main`** (no logfire/OTel here; revisit if/when the logfire branch merges)

**Schemas**
- [x] T-258: `agents/schemas.py` ‚Äî Pydantic output schemas: `ProfileOutput`, `ClientContextOutput`, `MatchingOutput`/`MatchItem`, `WriterOutput`, `GapAnalysisOutput`/`GapItem`, `DebriefOutput`, `CombinedOutput` (lenient: one required identifying field, extras ignored)

**Agent migration ‚Äî ALL agents**
- [x] T-259: `profile_agent` + `client_research_agent` via harness (validated output, console trace) ‚Äî primary acceptance target
- [x] T-260: `matching_agent` + `writer_agent` via harness (already `call_json` on `main`; no `pydantic_ai` to remove)
- [x] T-262: `gap_agent`, `combined_agent`, `debrief_agent` via harness; `persona_agent` via harness in text mode
- [n/a] T-261: Remove `pydantic_ai` dependency ‚Äî **N/A on `main`** (never present)
- [x] T-263: Orchestrator interface unchanged ‚Äî verified `run_proposal_pipeline()` / `handle_twin_message()` signatures intact, all modules import without cycles

**Harness tests** (`tests/test_harness.py`)
- [x] T-271: Output-validation retry ‚Äî invalid JSON then valid ‚Üí returns validated dict, exactly one retry
- [x] T-272: No-hallucination guardrail flags a fabricated skill absent from the profile (issue acceptance test)
- [x] T-274: Profile + Client Research run via the harness and produce schema-valid output
- [x] T-275: Text-mode harness returns the (stripped) string response
- [n/a] T-273: Rewrite matching/writer `_agent` mocks ‚Üí `MockLLMClient` ‚Äî **N/A on `main`** (tests already use `MockLLMClient`)

